comments: Mitchell (UTA) has his off-arm out during the drive but does not extend it further into the defender, Bridges (PHX), as he side-steps into his shot attempt.
Bridges (PHX) legally contests the shot attempt from Mitchell (UTA).
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of House Jr. (UTA) and some contact occurs to the defenders side as he fights over the top of the screen.
Mitchell (UTA) makes some contact with the left arm of Johnson (PHX) at the end of the drive but the contact does not impact Johnson's pass.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Bridges (PHX) and he firms up to absorb the contact during the screen.

Replay review of the personal foul called on Booker (PHX) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful. Prior to any contact from Booker (PHX), Johnson (PHX) makes illegal contact with the left arm of Gobert (UTA) and the contact does not occur during a power up to the basket.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Johnson (PHX) and turns slightly as he firms up during the screen. The contact to Johnson during the screen is marginal.
Bridges (PHX) briefly places and removes his hand from Mitchell's (UTA) arm during the screen and the contact is marginal.
During the loose ball, Bridges (PHX) swipes down and makes contact to Gobert's (UTA) arm. Any additional contact from the pair prior is deemed marginal.
Booker (PHX) reestablishes himself in bounds prior to receiving the pass from Crowder (PHX).
Gobert (UTA) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Crowder (PHX).
Booker (PHX) briefly places and removes a hand from the side of Mitchell (UTA) as the latter goes into his upward shooting motion.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Crowder (PHX) makes a bad pass and throws the ball over the head of Booker (PHX). Possession is correctly awarded to Utah.
Johnson (PHX) commits a take foul on Conley (UTA).
Gobert (UTA) steps backwards to avoid making contact with Booker's (PHX) lower body as the latter jumps slightly forwards during his shot attempt.
